Directory structure 

- bird : official bird, not modified
- bird/compiled : idem but compiled version
- conf-bird : configuration files for official bird daemon

- ourbird : our modified bird
- ourbird/compiled : idem but compiled version
- conf-ourbird : configuration files for our bird setup (with damping)

- log-dbg : log and debug files storage
- socket : bird unix sockets -> access via birdc

- mdfmt : feeder program (python)
- updates : updates for the feeder


Scripts

- start_bird.sh : start traditional bird with the topology
- start_ourbird.sh : start our bird with the topology, and route damping ON
- reset_all.sh : clean the logs, kill the daemons

Files

- eval-topo.ppt : the topology overview
